Entry.3: Started with Mr. McMillan (C. E. ) at Seaford.
Entry.20: P. N. for 10/- No. E. 347964 to Mr. Johnson (Clears up to
Entry.24: Sighted land at 10-15 am. Arrived Durban about 12 noon. Allowed on shore 3. 45 pm and marched into Durban (1. 75 miles) and granted leave till 11pm
Entry.25: Not finished coaling. Granted leave from 10 am till 2 pm. Sailed at 5-15 pm.
Entry.26: Very rough and keeping in sight of land.
Entry.27: Sighted lights of Cape Town at 7. 30pm. Lay in Bay till next morning (arr in bay 9. 30pm)
Entry.28: Route march in the morning. Sport in oval in the afternoon, concert and tea in the evening at Feather Market.
Entry.29:
Tram ride round lions head. 

Left Cape Town 6 am.
Entry.31: Sighted land about 6 pm (Freetown Sierra Leone) Lay off till next morning.
Entry.32: Went into bay not allowed ashore.
Entry.33: Went ashore in ships boat. Granted leave from 10 am till about 4 pm.
Entry.38: Received wireless message about 1 am. Ship turned back to Freetown.
Entry.39: Arrived back at Freetown Sierra Leone about 2 am.
Entry.40: Collier came alongside about 7 am First shift of our boys started coaling about 8. 30 am. Finished coaling about 12 noon. Total 820 tons.
Entry.41: Freetwon, Sierra Leone. B. W. A.
Entry.43:
Left Sierra Leone at 10. 30 am

Great cheering when we weighed anchor.
Entry.44:
Sighted troopships and escort at 8. 30 am, 5 transports and two Cruisers. At 9. 30 we met and formed into 3 lines (3 in each line) as follows

Entry.45:
Maribyrnong Camp

Reveille 3. 30 am. 

Left camp at 6am. and marched to a scot Vale station. Arrived there about 7 am and got special train to Port. Melb. (arr. P. M. about 8 am). Embarked on S. S. “Borda" (A30) at 10 am. 

Friends not allowed on pier till 12. 50 pm. 

Sailed at 1 pm

Memoranda
Entry.46: About 5 pm the Kent left us and all the transports went in different directions.
Entry.47: 30 10 destroyers met us but only one remained.
Entry.48: very rough spray coming on to the boat deck. Passed destroyer this morning and sometimes the waves went right over her. (45)
